	<h1 class="title">让全球 H&amp;M 门店大排长龙的亚历山大·王，是个这样的人</h1>
	<div class="author-date clearfix">					
			<div class="author clearfix">
					<span class="avatar x25 circle">
						<img src="/img/missing_face.png" alt="">
					</span>
				<span class="name">VANESSA FRIEDMAN</span>
			</div>
		<span class="date smart-date" data-originDate="2014-11-06 16:20:31 +0800"></span>
	</div>
	<div class="banner">
			<img src="/system/articles/articleshows/2169/medium/2169.jpeg?1436648549" alt="" />			
	</div>
	<!-- 传入参数：obj(aritcle, paper, card, mob) -->


